name: Cyber Angel Benten
desc: You can Ritual Summon this card with "Machine Angel Ritual". If this card destroys a monster by battle and sends it to the Graveyard: Inflict damage to your opponent equal to that monster's original DEF in the Graveyard. If this card is Tributed: You can add 1 LIGHT Fairy-Type monster from your Deck to your hand.
str2: Add 1 LIGHT Fairy-Type monster to hand

ocg.pack: Collectors Pack: Duelist of Flash Version
